4 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
5 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend Our Lady of Prompt Succor Church and
6 School on the occasion of the seventy-fifth Our Lady of Prompt Succor Tomato Festival and
7 does hereby encourage citizens to support local festivals that celebrate the rich culture and
8 heritage of local communities throughout the state.
